1138
01:22:45,894 --> 01:22:48,385
<i>Your love is mine</i>

1139
01:22:52,000 --> 01:22:53,399
OSCAR: Hey, Chloe!

1140
01:22:55,537 --> 01:22:57,266
This is you and me.

1141
01:22:58,573 --> 01:23:01,337
<i>I've got this feeling</i>

1142
01:23:01,609 --> 01:23:05,705
<i>That we'll always</i>
<i>be all right</i>

1143
01:23:06,081 --> 01:23:07,981
<i>Yeah</i>

1144
01:23:08,450 --> 01:23:11,681
