Who the fuck are you?

1245
01:33:14,355 --> 01:33:16,289
Harry Stevenson.

1246
01:33:16,357 --> 01:33:18,917
I don't think we've had the pleasure.

1247
01:33:19,560 --> 01:33:20,857
What's that?

1248
01:33:22,997 --> 01:33:24,794
What do you think?

1249
01:33:26,801 --> 01:33:28,564
Well, what's it for?

1250
01:33:29,303 --> 01:33:32,761
- For that whore that killed my boy.
- Now, wait a minute.

1251
01:33:32,840 --> 01:33:36,139
I was told that that was because of
a congenital heart defect.

1252
01:33:36,210 --> 01:33:39,338
I don't need to listen to that crap!
I got business here.

1253
01:33:41,782 --> 01:33:43,044
So do I.

1254
01:33:43,117 --> 01:33:44,106
(GROANS)

1255
01:33:46,354 --> 01:33:48,151
Now, listen to me.

1256
01:33:48,222 --> 01:33:51,316
You are not to bother that girl ever again.
You understand me?

1257
01:33:51,392 --> 01:33:53,587
You are not to blame her
for your miserable life.

1258
01:33:53,661 --> 01:33:58,997
You do, and I'll kill you myself. I swear it.
Now get the hell out of here. Go on!

1259
01:34:07,041 --> 01:34:08,372
Harry?

1260
01:34:08,676 --> 01:34:12,203
- It was the Bat, wasn't it?
- It's all right. He's gone.

1261
01:34:16,450 --> 01:34:18,884
- You okay?
- Yeah.

1262
01:34:31,098 --> 01:34:32,429
Chloe...

1263
01:34:36,437 --> 01:34:40,840
You asked me
if Esther and I would be your parents.

1264
01:34:47,782 --> 01:34:50,444
I thought you were just being kind
to an old man

1265
01:34:50,518 --> 01:34:54,249
after I told you about the death of my son,

1266
01:34:56,490 --> 01:34:58,321
so I didn't answer.

1267
01:35:00,294 --> 01:35:06,255
And I didn't know that you already knew
that terrible things were going to happen.

1268
01:35:13,441 --> 01:35:16,569
Esther and I want you to come
and live with us.

1269
01:35:18,045 --> 01:35:19,774
Be our little girl.

1270
01:35:28,756 --> 01:35:30,189
Say yes.

1271
01:35:31,525 --> 01:35:33,322
Please say yes.

1272
01:35:35,696 --> 01:35:36,754
Yes.

1273
01:35:38,232 --> 01:35:39,358
Yes.

1274
01:35:40,801 --> 01:35:41,790
(CRYING)

1275
01:35:47,575 --> 01:35:48,735
Yes.

1276
01:35:49,944 --> 01:35:55,041
Esther and I will give you and your baby
all the love we have left to give.

1277
01:35:58,519 --> 01:36:00,111
Let's go home.

1278
01:36:07,194 --> 01:36:10,425
<i>HARRY: The unexpected is always upon us.</i>

1279
01:36:11,866 --> 01:36:14,664
<i>And of all the gifts arrayed before me,</i>

1280
01:36:14,735 --> 01:36:19,399
<i>this one thought at this moment in my life</i>
<i>is the most precious.</i>

1281
01:36:21,175 --> 01:36:24,941
<i>And so, we begin again.</i>

